dc_title_s: Historical Salmonid Streams of the Russian River Basin, California, 1920-2000
dc_description_s: This line shapefile shows streams in the Russian River basin which have supported chinook, coho, or steelhead salmon. This layer includes data from surveys available from California Department of Fish and Game and the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers.This dataset is intended signify which streams in the Russian River basin have historically supported chinook, coho, or steelhead salmonids.
